
Davis Learning Center offers (Tutoring) academic help to all students K12 in reading, math, writing, study skills, and homework.

In their words, At Davis Learning, we are committed to having a positive impact in your childs life.  We understand that the classroom has a tremendous influence on shaping a person into adulthood, and our efforts are focused on increasing not only knowledge, but confidence and self worth.  Your childs success is our first priority.  Here, youll find a warm and inviting atmosphere, where children feel comfortable and safe.  We work with your schedule to provide Academic Support when you need it, after school or on Saturdays. Our professional, credentialed teachers assist in creating and continuously monitoring the right plan for your student.

